{{Expand Italian|date=August 2010|Teatro Quirino}}
[[File:Teatro Quirino.JPG|260px|thumbnail|Teatro Quirino]]
The '''Teatro Quirino''' is an [[opera]] [[opera house|house]] in [[Rome]] opened in 1871.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Sergio Rotondi|title=Il Teatro Quirino: l'architettura teatrale a Roma|publisher=Kappa, 1983}}</ref> It hosted the premiere of [[Pietro Mascagni]]'s operetta ''[[Sì (operetta)|Sì]]''.

